com.github.jukkakarvanen.kafka.streams.test

Class TestRecord<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.jukkakarvanen.kafka.streams.test.TestRecord<K,V>

  • public class TestRecord<K,V>
extends java.lang.Object
    A key/value pair to be send to or received from Kafka. This also consists header information and a timestamp. If record do not contain a timestamp, the TestInputTopic will use auto advance time logic.
